Run the server in the sql workbench
 
Run the code by the following command

filename: application_4a.cpp

g++ application_4a.cpp -o application -lmysqlcppconn

then run the executable by the command

./application <servername> <username> <password>

example
servername=tcp://localhost:3306
username=root
password=******

Code has a while loop which enables user to interact with it multiple time 
if teaching tuple already exists with different classromm we are updating that classroom to user given input

